    ],
    "text": "Investigations were initiated by the Pallewela Police Station on the night of 03.04.2026, following information received regarding a fatal assault carried out with a sharp weapon in the Banduragoda area within the Pallewela Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      87.37,
      473.38,
      100.65
    ],
    "text": "The deceased has been identified as a 60-year-old resident of Banduragoda.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      115.21,
      516.34,
      156.09
    ],
    "text": "The motive for the crime has not yet been determined, and the suspect involved has fled the area. The body remains at the scene under police guard while further investigations are being conducted by the Pallewela Police to apprehend the suspect.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
